                    We provide end-to-end digital solutions designed specifically for small businesses
                    looking to establish or enhance their online presence.
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success fa-2x me-3"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Affordable Pricing</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">Transparent packages that fit small business budgets</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success fa-2x me-3"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Fast Delivery</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">Most projects completed within 2-4 weeks</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success fa-2x me-3"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">Ongoing Support</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">We're here even after your project launches</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-body p-5 text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-handshake fa-4x text-primary mb-4"></i>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Not Sure Where to Start?</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
